\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American has continued her impressive form into the latter half of the year, winning four consecutive races - including last weekend's Grand Final in Dubai - to claim the first-ever T100 title and the $210,000 cash bonus.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998078715364, \"rank\": 1.4258926798025055e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\", \"score\": 0.9999981687709292, \"rank\": 1.83123143245093e-06, \"text\": \"Grand Final\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"score\": 0.9999999914389264, \"rank\": 8.11003330084826e-09, \"text\": \"Dubai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the brutal weather conditions in the United Arab Emirates\\u00a0evidently took their toll on Knibb after she had pulled clear of her competition with little over two kilometres to go.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8436097304433088, \"rank\": 0.18538135445301462, \"text\": \"United Arab Emirates\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.912548639869311e-12, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the cameras approaching to film her final moments, the American revealed that she had soiled herself midway through the race.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998078715364, \"rank\": 1.4258926798025055e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just s*** myself.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So can you not get my a**?'\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she asked the camera operator who quickly obliged before adjusting the shot.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Taylor Knibbs wins T100 triathlon title with a dominant performance while sh*thing herself.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00b2pic.twitter.com/bL97LFmaV6  Despite that, Knibb remained focused and stormed to the line in first place, finishing the race almost two minutes ahead of silver medallist Julie Derron.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.912548639869311e-12, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterwards she revealed that the race - a combination of a 2 km open-water swim, an 80 km bike ride, and an 18 km run - had proved difficult from start to finish.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I woke up and messaged my coach that I just feel rough, and I am like, \\\"Oh, this is going to be a bad day,' Knibb admitted.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.912548639869311e-12, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, I was kind of shocked!\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It only came together in the last 3km when everyone else fell apart, but it was very step-by-step.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was brutal out there.'\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Knibb only needed to finish second on the day to guarantee her world title but remained on task despite the pre-race nerves from those around her.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1903, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.912548639869311e-12, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think my dad was more nervous today than me\\u2026 I was like, \\\"Oh wow, you are really nervous, like it's kind of spreading\\\",' she added.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I have a fantastic team of individuals and then I have a lot of sponsors and so it's just a huge team effort and I am very grateful for everyone who supports me and believes in me.'\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Ashleigh Gentle, meanwhile, who finished third in Dubai and second in the end-of-season standings, lauded the ability of Knibb after her stunning triumph.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2375, \"end\": 2384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.5743162139320334, \"rank\": 0.5632193678927893, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Gentle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ashleigh Gentle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Gentle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashleigh_Gentle\"}, {\"begin\": 2437, \"end\": 2442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"score\": 0.9999999914389264, \"rank\": 8.11003330084826e-09, \"text\": \"Dubai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\"}, {\"begin\": 2508, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.912548639869311e-12, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Taylor has just been dominating and when you are racing an athlete like that, it is sometimes really difficult to truly believe that you can beat them,' she said.\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I had this little fire in my belly\\u2026 I have no reason to believe that I can beat her, but I am on the start line and that means I have got a chance, so I just had to believe that.\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did not beat her but feel like I was a step closer today and did everything I could to try and get there.'\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Sir Chris Hoy and wife Sarra explain how they told children their devastating diagnoses  ArrowMORE:'There is hope' - Sir Chris Hoy reveals target to live beyond his cancer diagnosis  ArrowMORE:Olympics breakdancing icon Raygun U-turns on shock retirement announcement  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}, {\"begin\": 3257, \"end\": 3266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  P